  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package records an Accepted decision despite several credibility factors carrying no requiredLevel or achievedLevel, instantiating the W-CON-01 factor-decision inconsistency weakener.",
