    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed available evidence and determined that the CFD hemolysis model provides sufficient basis for regulatory submission. Monte Carlo UQ results demonstrate hemolysis predictions remain below the clinical threshold across sampled operating conditions. The team considers the overall evidence package adequate for the intended use, noting that several factor-level evaluations remain incomplete but judging residual uncertainty to be manageable given the conservative UQ bounds reported.",
